@node INST "FOUR IN ONE  HELP:   How to install 4in1"

  The installation of 4in1 is simple:
  just copy the executable in your C: drawer.

  You can make it resident using:

    resident c:4in1

@endnode

@node HW "FOUR IN ONE  HELP:   HardWare needed to run 4in1"

  Nothing expecial,just an old A500.
  The program should work with this @{" system software " link SW} 
@endnode

